title: What picture formats and resolutions does my phone support?
answer:
Your phone supports JPG files at a maximum of 3264x2448 (8 MP). 

 1. Rear camera: 8 MP (3264x2448), 6 MP (3264x1836), 5 MP (2592x1952), 3.8 MP (2592x1456), and 0.3 MP (640x480). 

 1. Front camera: 5 MP (2592x1952), 3.8 MP (2592x1456), 1.3 MP (1280x960), 0.9 MP (1280x720), and 0.3 MP (640x480).
